                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6936" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1079</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8499 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逐金冒险“牛吞象”——天山生物并购之殇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Going for gold to risk &quot;Null and swallowing elephant&quot;-the death of Tianshan Biological M&amp;A</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">夏婧，罗雨，王露</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆天山畜牧生物工程股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天山生物；企业并购；并购动因；并购风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tianshan Biological Company; Enterprise M&amp;A; Motivation of M&amp;A; M&amp;A risk;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018年4月，天山生物跨界强势收购了营业收入、净利润等均高于自身的大象广告，但并购完成半年后，大象广告涉嫌合同诈骗、资金挪用、违规担保的一连串丑闻相继曝出。至此，收购方天山生物出现巨额亏损，股东背负巨额债务，天山生物收购大象广告以失败告终，公司转型失败；而被收购方大象广告也四分五裂，多地分支机构或解散或停滞，掌门人陈德宏深陷囹圄、锒铛入狱。本案例通过介绍并购各方的情况，分析了天山生物并购大象广告事件中双方的动机，梳理了并购的方案、过程和结果等。以天山生物并购案作为案例，旨在运用企业并购的相关理论分析并购双方的动因和并购失败的原因，思考如何降低跨界并购存在的潜在风险，同时探讨与之相关的企业并购战略问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In April 2018, Tianshan Biotech cross-border strong acquisition of Daxiang Advertising revenue, net profit and other higher than its own, but six months after the completion of the merger, Daxiang Advertising suspected contract fraud, funds embezzlement, violation of guarantee a series of scandals have been exposed. At this point, the acquirer Tianshan Biotech losses, shareholders bear a huge amount of debt, Tianshan Biotech acquisition of Elephant Advertising ended in failure, the company’s transformation failed; The acquired company Daxiang Advertising was also disintegrated, with many branches disbanded or stalled, and chief Chen Dehong is deeply in jail. This case introduces the situation of all parties in the M&amp;A, analyzes the motivation of both sides of Tianshan Biological M&amp;A of Elephant Advertising event, and combs the plan, process and results of the M&amp;A. Taking the merger of Tianshan Biological as an example, this paper aims to analyze the motivations of both parties and the reasons for the failure of M&amp;A by using the relevant theories of enterprise M&amp;A, consider how to reduce the potential risks in the process of M&amp;A, and discuss the related issues of enterprise M&amp;A strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略环境分析、PEST理论；跨界并购定义、动机；并购风险分析；信息不对称理论、尽职调查；并购启示</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
